data.description: Escape to this charming cabin nestled on 2.47 private acres in the heart of the North Georgia mountains. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and breathtaking panoramic views, this tranquil getaway offers the perfect blend of comfort and natural beauty. Step inside to discover a cozy living space with rustic decor and modern amenities. The fully equipped kitchen is ideal for preparing home-cooked meals, while the spacious bedrooms provide a peaceful haven for rest and relaxation. Enjoy your morning coffee on the expansive deck as you soak in the stunning vistas of the surrounding mountains. This property offers easy access to a variety of outdoor activities and attractions. Explore nearby hiking trails, visit local wineries, or take a scenic drive to the charming town of Helen for shopping and dining. Whether you're seeking adventure or simply a quiet retreat, this mountain oasis has something for everyone. Book your showing today!
